This test is described in the Users Guide.

The test's operation as a  "unit test" is not
yet fully documented in the U.G. For this, a file
unitTest_0000 will be generated that contains
either SUCCESS or FAILURE, plus some additional
summary information on changes in total mass
and momenta.  SUCCESS or FAILURE are determined
based on the following tolerance runtime parameters:
   PARAMETER sim_massTol          REAL
   PARAMETER sim_momXTol          REAL
   PARAMETER sim_momYTol          REAL
   PARAMETER sim_momZTol          REAL


A movie generated from the FLASH4 sink momentum test can be found here:
  http://www.ita.uni-heidelberg.de/~chfeder/pubs/sinks/Federrath_flash_momsinks.mp4

This website contains movies and tests for the sink particles:
  http://www.ita.uni-heidelberg.de/~chfeder/pubs/sinks/sinks.shtml?lang=en
